quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  33,23,mominoun mein kitney hi aisay shakhs hain ke jo iqraar onhon ne khuda sekiya tha is ko sach kar dekhaya. to un mein baaz aisay hain jo apni Nazar se farigh hogaye aur baaz aisay hain ke intzaar kar rahay hain aur onhon ne ( apne qoul ko ) zara bhi nahi badla
  33,24,taakay khuda schon ko unn ki sachaai ka badla day aur mnafqon ko chahay to azaab day aur ( chahay ) to unn par meharbani kere. be shak khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  33,25,aur jo kafir they unn ko khuda ne phair diya woh apne ghusse mein ( bharay hue they ) kuch bhalai haasil nah kar sakay. aur khuda mominoun ko larai ke baray mein kaafi howa. aur khuda taaqatwar ( aur ) zabardast hai
  33,26,aur ahal kitaab mein se jinhon ne unn ki madad ki thi unn ko unn ke qlaon se utaar diya aur unn ke dilon mein dehshat daal di. to ktnon ko tum qatal kar dete they aur ktnon ko qaid kar lete they
  33,27,aur unn ki zameen aur un ke gharon aur un ke maal ka aur is zameen ka jis mein tum ne paon bhi nahi rakha tha tum ko waris bana diya. aur khuda har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai
  33,28,ae paighambar apni biwion se keh do ke agar tum duniya ki zindagi aur is ki zeenat vaaraysh ki khawastgah ho to aao mein tumhe kuch maal dun aur achi terhan se rukhsat kardoon
  33,29,aur agar tum khuda aur is ke paighambar aur aqibat ke ghar ( yani bahisht ) ki tallab-gaar ho to tum mein jo نneko karikarne wali hain unn ke liye khuda ne ajar azeem tayyar kar rakha hai
  33,30,ae paighambar ki byoyo tum mein se jo koi Sarih na shaista ( alfaaz keh kar rasool allah ko aeza dainay ki ) harkat kere gi. is ko dunne saza di jaye gi. aur yeh ( baat ) khuda ko aasaan hai
